{
  "stem": "15396.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And actually I did it by-- just by signing papers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I didn't have to go to the camp or anything and do it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just outside of Paris.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think beyond Lucien, or somewhere like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was what the French-- which we call-- we learned later on were concentration . camps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was a detention place for undesirable foreigners and things like that, which meant they were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I have to say that sometimes the French did very, very courageous things with-- with them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't-- I don't think the picture of Vichy was-- was always the complete description of the French.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There-- there were lots of them, of course, who were.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were two or three kinds of collaborators.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "First place, the fifth column, you know, when there were retreats and all were dreadful.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They were doing everything they could to-- but they could have been Alsatian, or we don't know what, but doing everything they could to, you know, stir up problems and all.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But the-- it was the opportunist who wanted to get along because they knew the Germans were going to run things, and then the cowards who just did it because they were afraid.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I suppose there were some who thought, well, it's the lesser of the evils.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we never discussed it with them, because we dodged these people as much as we could.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I couldn't possibly pass judgment or-- I don't know how they really felt because we never talked to them.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We dodged them as much as we could.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The minute the ambulance corps thing started, we no-- I--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, soon after the-- after the war started.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were attached to French units.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
